{"tid":693244,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"卡利奧斯緋聞女友收死亡威脅！歐聯後被瘋狂辱罵","createTime":"2018-06-07T10:12:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-07T10:50:23.000Z","uid":147522,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1ff8e42baf98ec3f046c7df91a073d651cf7a89e","tid":693244,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T10:12:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/07/181213_0137e472a51557f577a0cfbd592076da.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F07%2F181213_0137e472a51557f577a0cfbd592076da.png&h=035aecfa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國4頻道真人秀節目《車路士製造》女星羅斯曾和利物浦門將卡利奧斯傳出緋聞，但卡利奧斯歐聯決賽犯錯後，有人威脅要捅死她。　<br />\n<br />\n　　27歲的羅斯幾週前曾被拍到和卡利奧斯在一起，她表示：「本週我遭到了非常過分的辱罵，最常見的是&lsquo;婊子&rsquo;。有人威脅捅死我，並殺死我的家人，他們還說我的家人已經死了，讓我自殺，還有被俄羅斯黑幫盯上等等。」<br />\n<br />\n　　「我一笑了之，儘可能地刪除這些評論，因為我認為他們絕對是一群瘋子。」<br />\n<br />\n　　據悉卡利奧斯目前的女友叫格蕾絲，羅斯稱：「我不知道俄羅斯媒體是怎麼罵我的，但我去年都是單身。」"},{"pid":"d55a30f362f3ea60e0204265361074d1475c28e0","tid":693244,"uid":134458,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T10:13:37.000Z","msg":"我都想捅佢"},{"pid":"88d39a9489995591bed8273cfaf286d7e6a2b37c","tid":693244,"uid":531,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T10:14:21.000Z","msg":"原來佢揸開細波，難怪接唔到巴利球遠射"},{"pid":"133bfb44c95645dafca6ee6334f63c051488dcee","tid":693244,"uid":47268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T10:25:06.000Z","msg":"我都想吉佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/40.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c82217573e22dc081f07fd93c65af45847f5aac4","tid":693244,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T10:26:08.000Z","msg":"車路士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"001d59787e9701e2a1ae7dc483989eda108e51dc","tid":693244,"uid":24925,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20